&lt;- molds dropable, great caster armor) and runes. <br>
<br>
I've seen ornate armor parts for sale already, so expect more to show up in bazaar soon.<br>
<br>
Elemental Planes also drop parts for awesome dropable caster gear. (60hp/mana some stats/resist efect: mana preservation IV primary/secondary/range) - expect lots of such items to show up in bazaar soon.<br>
